The paper is about Natural Language Processing (NLP) and related fields such as Artificial Intelligence (AI) and Machine Learning (ML). Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses neural graph-based networks and non-neural classifiers, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also mentions reading list generation, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the paper mentions a dataset, which could also suggest cs.DL (Deep Learning) as a possible category.
